K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215a-0: @215a yi dvags mo kha 'bar ma dbugs dbyungs ba'i gtor ma'i cho ga //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215a-1: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215a-2: de nas bcom ldan 'das yul ser skya na shing n+ye gro dha'i kun dga' ra ba na dge slong gi dge 'dun chen po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215a-3: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen po dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215a-4: sems can gyi tshogs chen po dang thabs cig tu bzhugs te chos ston to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215a-5: de nas kun dga' bo dben par 'dug ste nang du yang dag 'jog cing rtse gcig tu yid la byed pas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215a-6: chos mngon gsum du byed pa na mtshan mo nam gyi cha smad la de'i mdun du yi dvags mo kha 'bar ma 'dug nas smras pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215a-9: yi dvags kyi gnas 'dir skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215a-14: gal te nang pa yi dvags gangg'a'i klung gyi bye ma khrag khrig phrag 'bum gyi bye ma snyed dag la yi dvags re re la yang zas dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-0: skom @215b yul ma ga dha'i bre bo che bdun bdun tsam byin te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-1: bram ze'i drang srong 'bum yang tshim par byas la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-2: bdag gi ming gis dkon mchog gsum la mchod pa byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-3: de ltar na khyod kyi tshe yang phyir nur bar 'gyur la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-4: bdag kyang yi dvags kyi 'jig rten nas shi 'phos te mtho ris kyi 'jig rten du skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-5: de nas kun dga' bos yi dvags mo kha 'bar ma rid cing mdog ngan la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-9: ral pa'i phung po g-yengs pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-10: spu dang sen mo ring ba mthong ste; tshig mi snyan cing yid du mi 'ong ba de thos nas skrag cing sdangs te spu zing zhes byas nas /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-11: stan las langs te shin tu rings pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-12: shin tu myur ba'i shugs kyis bcom ldan 'das ga la ba der song ste phyin nas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs la phyag 'tshal te 'dar bzhin du 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-15: bde bar gshegs pa skyabs mdzad du gsol /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-16: bdag ni gnangs srog 'gum par 'gyur lags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:215b-18: bdag gis yi dvags mo kha 'bar ma mthong ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-0: bdag gis rten thabs ci mchis zhes smras nas de'i mchid nas gal te khyod @216a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-1: kyis yi dvags gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma khrag khrig phrag 'bum gyi bye ma snyed dag chim par byas te //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-2: bram ze'i drang srong 'bum yang tshim par byas na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-3: de ltar na khyod kyi tshe phyir nur bar 'gyur ro zhes mchi na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-5: de ji ltar bsgrub par bgyi ba bka' stsal du gsol //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-6: de nas bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa sh'akya thub pas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la 'di skad ces bka' stsal te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-8: gang gis khyod yi dvags rnams dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-9: bram ze'i drang srong rnams tshim par byed par 'gyur ba'i thabs yod kyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-12: thams cad du 'od dang ldan pa rgya chen shugs ldan zhes bya ba'i gzungs yod do //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-13: des byin pa tsam gyis yi dvags gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma khrag khrig phrag 'bum gyi bye ma snyed dag tshim par 'gyur te; yi dvags dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-14: bram ze'i drang srong re re la zas dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-15: skom yul ma ga dha'i bre bo bdun bdun byin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-17: sngon nga bram zer gyur ba na byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'jig rten dbang phyug dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216a-18: de bzhin gshegs pa 'jig rten dbang phyug 'od las ngas bzung ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-1: bram ze'i drang srong grangs su bgrang ba mang ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-2: ches mang ba'ang ngas zas dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-3: skom gyis tshim par byas te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-4: de dag thams cad yi dvags kyi 'jig rten nas shi 'phos nas lha'i 'jig rten du skyes so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-6: khyod kyis zungs la ngo lon gyis shig /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-7: na ma: sarba ta th'a ga ta aa ba lo ki te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-8: aom sam bha ra sam bha ra h'um/
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-10: 'di yi dvags kyi gtor ma la lan bdun bzlas brjod byas nas lag pa brkyang ste drung du sbyin par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-11: se gol yang brdab par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-13: byin ma thag tu phyogs bzhi'i yi dvags gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma khrag khrig phrag 'bum phrag gi bye ma snyed dag tshim par byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-14: yi dvags re re la yang yul ma ga dha'i bre bo bdun bdun byin par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-15: de dag kyang zos pa tsam gyis yi dvags kyi 'jig rten nas shi 'phos nas lha rnams kyi nang du skye bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-20: dge bsnyen ma rnams la rtag tu rgyun mi 'chad par khor zug tu bsnyad par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:216b-22: bsod nams kyi phung po dang ldan par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-0: de bzhin gshegs pa bye ba phrag 'bum gyi @217a *//
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-1: bsod nams kyi phung po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-2: rtag tu mi ma yin pa rgyu ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-5: grul bum la sogs pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-9: yi dvags rnams kyis mi mthong bar 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-11: brtson 'grus dang yang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-13: gzi brjid dang ldan pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-14: dran pa dang ldan par yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-15: bram ze'i drang srong tshim par byed pa 'dod pa des ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-18: snod bkang ba la lan bdun bzlas brjod byas la 'bab chu ga la yod pa'i gnas der sbyin par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-20: bram ze'i drang srong gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma khrag khrig 'bum phrag du ma'i bye ma snyed dag lha'i bza' ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-21: btung ba rnams kyis tshim par byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-22: bram ze'i drang srong de dag kyang dbang po tshim par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-23: de dag thams cad kyis aom bde legs su gyur cig ces bya ba'i sgra 'byin par byed la /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-24: sems can de dag kyang bsam pa yongs su dag par 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217a-25: bram ze'i gzi brjid dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217b-0: rtag tu tshangs par spyod par @217b yang 'gyur te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217b-1: de bzhin gshegs pa gang+g'a'i klung gi bye ma khrag khrig phrag 'bum gyi bye ma snyed dag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba dang ldan par yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217b-2: rtag tu dgra thams cad zhig par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217b-7: skom gyi yo byad la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas brjod byas la sangs rgyas dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217b-15: dge ba snyen ma des phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi zhing gi sangs rgyas dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217b-17: dge 'dun la lha'i mchod pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217b-18: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa'i mchog gis mchod pa byas par 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217b-21: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis dgongs shing lung bstan pa dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217b-22: lha thams cad kyis kun tu srung bar yang 'gyur ro //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-035:217b-24: song la ngo lon yang gyis shig /
